code: @Override protected void before() throws Throwable {     log.info("Starting embedded broker[{}] on {}", brokerId, tcpConnectorUri).     brokerService.start(). }

@Override protected void after() {     try {         log.info("Stopping embedded broker[{}]", brokerId).         brokerService.stop().     } catch (Exception e) {         throw new RuntimeException("Exception shutting down broker service", e).     } }
